                             \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eI\u0026#39;m on my third and probably final 3DS console, with my New 3DS XL sleeping soundly beside my bed every night, but many people missed out on Nintendo\u0026#39;s amazing little machine and haven\u0026#39;t experienced the magic of autostereoscopy—glasses-free 3D.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe monitors also feature Glare-Free technology, certified by Underwriters Laboratories (UL), to reduce reflections. To prevent screen burn-in, Samsung includes its OLED Safeguard+ system with a Dynamic Cooling System with a special Pulsating Heat Pipe for better heat control.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe gameplay is smooth and responsive with a super-fast 0.03ms response time and support for AMD FreeSync Premium Pro and NVIDIA G-SYNC Compatible. The monitor also has a sleek metal design and built-in Core Lighting+.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe last model in the Odyssey series is the Odyssey G9 (G91F model), which offers an ultra-wide gaming experience on a massive 49-inch Dual QHD curved screen (1000R curvature). This monitor focuses on immersion with a 144Hz refresh rate, 1ms response time, and AMD FreeSync Premium Pro support.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe Odyssey G9 also has VESA DisplayHDR 600 and HDR10+ GAMING for vivid, detailed visuals. The Odyssey G9 makes multitasking easier with Picture-by-Picture and Picture-in-Picture modes, and its Auto Source Switch+ feature automatically detects and displays connected devices.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eYou can buy each of these monitors on the official Samsung website today. The \u003ca href=\"https://shop-links.co/link/?exclusive=1\u0026amp;publisher_slug=howtogeek\u0026amp;u1=UUhtgUeUpU2012323\u0026amp;article_name=Samsung%27s+Glasses-Free+3D+Gaming+Monitors+Are+Now+Available\u0026amp;article_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2Fsamsung-odyssey-3d-monitor-release%2F\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fmonitors%2Fgaming%2F27-inch-odyssey-3d-g90xf-4k-165hz-gaming-monitor-sku-ls27fg900xnxza%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\"\u003eOdyssey G9 3D 4K Gaming Monitor\u003c/a\u003e costs $1,999.99, the \u003ca href=\"https://shop-links.co/link/?exclusive=1\u0026amp;publisher_slug=howtogeek\u0026amp;u1=UUhtgUeUpU2012323\u0026amp;article_name=Samsung%27s+Glasses-Free+3D+Gaming+Monitors+Are+Now+Available\u0026amp;article_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2Fsamsung-odyssey-3d-monitor-release%2F\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fmonitors%2Fgaming%2F27-inch-odyssey-oled-g8-g81sf-4k-240hz-gaming-monitor-sku-ls27fg810snxza%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\"\u003eOdyssey G8 4K Gaming Monitor\u003c/a\u003e does not have a cost announced yet, and the \u003ca href=\"https://shop-links.co/link/?exclusive=1\u0026amp;publisher_slug=howtogeek\u0026amp;u1=UUhtgUeUpU2012323\u0026amp;article_name=Samsung%27s+Glasses-Free+3D+Gaming+Monitors+Are+Now+Available\u0026amp;article_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2Fsamsung-odyssey-3d-monitor-release%2F\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fmonitors%2Fgaming%2F49-inch-odyssey-g9-g91f-dqhd-144hz-gaming-monitor-sku-ls49fg910enxza%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\"\u003eOdyssey G9 Curved Gaming Monitor\u003c/a\u003e costs $999.99.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eSource: \u003ca href=\"https://news.samsung.com/us/2025-samsung-odyssey-gaming-monitors-now-available-next-phase-of-gaming/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSamsung\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n               